📁 File Structure Overview:
parkreview0.3/
├── parkreview0303/               # Django project root
│   ├── manage.py                 # 🐍 Python - Django management script
│   ├── parkreview/               # Main application folder
│   │   ├── models.py             # 🐍 Python - Database models
│   │   ├── views.py              # 🐍 Python - View controllers
│   │   ├── urls.py               # 🐍 Python - URL routing
│   │   ├── static/               # Static assets
│   │   │   ├── css/              # 🎨 CSS files
│   │   │   │   ├── style.css     # Main styles
│   │   │   │   ├── map-fix.css   # Map-specific styles
│   │   │   │   └── rating-fix.css # Rating-specific styles
│   │   │   ├── js/               # 📜 JavaScript files
│   │   │   │   └── map-utils.js  # Map utilities
│   │   │   └── images/           # Image assets
│   │   └── templates/            # 🌐 HTML templates
│   │       ├── base.html         # Base template
│   │       ├── home.html         # Home page
│   │       └── parks/            # Park-related templates
│   │           ├── detail.html   # Park detail page
│   │           ├── map.html      # Map view
│   │           └── recensioni.html # Reviews page
│   └── parkreview0303/           # Django project settings
└── staticfiles/                  # Collected static files
